{
  "name": "Connection Recommender",
  "description": "Recommends professional connections and generates personalized outreach strategies based on career graph data",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "webhook_input",
      "type": "source/webhook",
      "config": {
        "path": "/connections",
        "method": "POST"
      },
      "position": { "x": 0, "y": 200 }
    },
    {
      "id": "extract_data",
      "type": "transform/json-extract",
      "config": {
        "fields": ["transitionMakers", "intermediateContacts", "currentRole", "targetRole"]
      },
      "position": { "x": 200, "y": 200 }
    },
    {
      "id": "generate_outreach",
      "type": "llm/anthropic",
      "config": {
        "model": "claude-sonnet-4-20250514",
        "system_prompt": "You are a professional networking strategist. Given data about people who have made similar career transitions (from a professional graph database), create personalized outreach recommendations.\n\nFor each connection:\n1. Explain WHY this person is valuable to connect with\n2. Suggest a specific, non-generic outreach message\n3. Recommend conversation topics based on their background\n4. Prioritize connections by relevance\n\nBe authentic — avoid sounding robotic or transactional.\n\nRespond in JSON format:\n{\n  \"connections\": [{\n    \"name\": \"...\",\n    \"company\": \"...\",\n    \"role\": \"...\",\n    \"priority\": \"high/medium/low\",\n    \"reason\": \"Why connect with this person\",\n    \"outreach_message\": \"Suggested first message\",\n    \"talking_points\": [\"...\"],\n    \"outreach_tip\": \"Strategy advice\"\n  }],\n  \"networking_strategy\": \"Overall approach for this career transition\"\n}",
        "temperature": 0.5,
        "max_tokens": 2048
      },
      "position": { "x": 400, "y": 200 }
    },
    {
      "id": "output",
      "type": "output/webhook-response",
      "config": {
        "content_type": "application/json"
      },
      "position": { "x": 600, "y": 200 }
    }
  ],
  "edges": [
    { "from": "webhook_input", "to": "extract_data", "output": "default", "input": "default" },
    { "from": "extract_data", "to": "generate_outreach", "output": "default", "input": "default" },
    { "from": "generate_outreach", "to": "output", "output": "default", "input": "default" }
  ]
}
